summary: With This Mod All The Executioner Items Are Craftable
descriptionHtml:
Craftable Executioner Items

With This Mod All The Executioner Items Are Craftable.
U Can Craft The Boots, Gloves, Hood, Armor, And Axe At The Skyforge.

The Executioner Outfit Can Be Found Under The Leather Section.
The Axe Under The Iron Section.

Everything Can Be Upgraded.
The Executioner Outfit With 1 Leather.
The Axe With 1 Iron Ingot.

How To Install: Put The File In The Skyrim Data Folder.
author: JP0005
